INSERT INTO `sxgg` VALUES ('610', '43', '北京市海淀区人民法院', 'Haidian District Beijing people\'s court', null, null, '（2016）京0108执6608号', '(2016) Beijing, No. 0108, No. 6608', '判决如下： 一、？ 准许孙毅开与王向毅离婚。 二、？ 婚生女孙珑耘由王向毅抚养，孙毅开自二○○八年十二月起每月给付抚养费三千元，至孙珑耘十八周岁时止。 三、？ 孙毅开于本判决生效后三十日内给付王向毅北京市海淀区安宁庄西路房屋还贷折价款七万七千六百二十八元五角。 四、？ 北京市宣武区香炉营东巷二号院芳芷苑五号楼M座四层四○四号房屋归王向毅所有，对应车位（车位号B1B039）由王向毅使用，购该套房屋的剩余贷款由王向毅自行偿还，王向毅于本判决生效后三十日内给付购房、车位折价款二十八万九千元。 五、？ 孙毅开婚后取得华为技术有限公司内部股净值十三万零九百四十元、二○○七年离职补助十八万九千四百零二元八角、二○○七年分红款五十万四千七百四十七元二角七分、华闻传媒股份五千股及奥迪A4轿车（车牌号京J19737）归孙毅开所有，孙毅开于本判决生效后三十日内给付王向毅对应财产折价款五十六万六千八百五十二元。 六、？ 王向毅名下工商银行存款四百七十五元九角一分(账号0200208801026478947)、招商银行存款七百八十九元八角二分（账号6225800100632099）归王向毅所有；孙毅开名下招商银行存款五百七十三元八角八分（账号6225881011759288）、存款一百一十九元八角五分（账号6225881012005756）归孙毅开所有。 七、？ 北京市宣武区香炉营东巷二号院芳芷苑五号楼M座四层四○四号房屋内西门子三门电冰箱一台、TCL五十厘米液晶电视一台、西门子全自动洗衣机一台、皮沙发两个归王向毅所有；松下摄像机一台、创维八十一厘米液晶电视一台归孙毅开所有，于本判决生效后三十日内执行。 八、？ 驳回孙毅开、王向毅的其他诉讼请求。 如未按本判决指定的期间履行给付金钱义务，应当依照《中华人民共和国民事诉讼法》第二百三十二条之规定，加倍给付迟延履行期间的债务利息。 保全费五千元，由孙毅开负担二千五百元，于本判决生效后七日内交纳；由王向毅负担二千五百元，已缴纳。 案件受理费一万五千三百元，由王向毅负担一万零三百元，其中七十五元已交纳，余款于本判决生效后七日内交至本院；由孙毅开负担五千元，于本判决生效后七日内交至本院。 如不服本判决，可在判决书送达之日起十五日内，向本院递交上诉状，并按对方当事人的人数提交副本，交纳上诉案件受理费一万五千三百元，上诉于北京市第一中级人民法院。如在上诉期满后七日内未交纳上诉案件受理费的，按自动撤回上诉处理。', 'The verdict is as follows: 1 Allow Sun Yi and Wang Xiangyi divorce. Two,? Sun Longyun married a girl raised by Wang Xiangyi, Sun Yi since two hours, eight years from December three thousand yuan per month alimony payments to the sun, Longyun eighteen years time. Three,? Sun Yi opened in the thirty days after the entry into force of the judgment, Haidian District, Beijing, west of the city of peace road, West Road, the housing loan discount of $five yuan. Four,? Beijing Xuanwu District City Hospital No. two incense Ying Dong Xiang Fang Zhiyuan No. five building M block four layer four, four houses owned by Wang Xiangyi, the corresponding parking (parking number B1B039) used by Wang Xiangyi, the remaining loan to buy the houses by Wang Xiangyi to repay, Wang Xiangyi in thirty days after the effective date of this judgment in the payment of the purchase, car discount paragraph two hundred and eighty-nine thousand yuan. Five,? Sun Yi married HUAWEI Technology Co. Ltd. internal shares of the net value of one hundred and thirty thousand nine hundred and forty yuan, two hours, seven year turnover one hundred and eighty-nine thousand four hundred and two yuan subsidy, two hours, seven years 1.80 dividends paid five hundred and four thousand seven hundred and forty-seven yuan in 27 Fen, the Chinese news media shares five thousand shares and Audi A4 car (license plate number J19737 Beijing) to open all the Sun Yi, Sun Yi to open after the effective date of this judgment within thirty days of payment Wang Xiangyi corresponding property paid five hundred and sixty-six thousand eight hundred and fifty-two yuan discount. Six,? The name of the Wang Xiangyi commercial bank deposits four hundred and seventy-five yuan 91 Fen (number 020020880102647894), China Merchants Bank deposits seven hundred and eighty-nine yuan 82 Fen (number 6225800100632099) owned by Wang Xiangyi; Sun Yi opened under the name of China Merchants Bank deposits five hundred and seventy-three yuan 88 Fen (number 6225881011759288), 85 Fen (one hundred and nineteen yuan deposit account number 6225881012005756) to open all the sun yi. Seven,? Beijing Xuanwu District City Hospital No. two incense Ying Dong Xiang Fang Zhiyuan No. five building M block four layer four, four houses in SIEMENS three door refrigerator, a TCL fifty cm LCD TV, SIEMENS automatic washing machine, a leather sofa two Wang Xiangyi all Panasonic camera;', '孙毅开', 'Sunyikai', 0xE585A8E983A8E69CAAE5B1A5E8A18C, 'All unfulfilled', '(2008)海民初字第00185号', '(2008) sea min Chu Zi No. 00185', '北京市海淀区人民法院', 'Haidian District Beijing people\'s court', '1482249600000', '北京', null, null, '1466956800000', '其他有履行能力而拒不履行生效法律文书确定义务', 'Others have the ability to perform and refuse to fulfill the obligations of the legal documents', 'c2016110108zhi66