INSERT INTO `sxgg` VALUES ('620', null, '福泉市人民法院   黔南州中级人民法院', 'Fuquan City People\'s court Qiannan intermediate people\'s court', null, null, '（2016）黔2702执157号', '(2016) Guizhou No. 2702 holding No. 157', '　　　　一、由被告贵州福泉小河口汽贸有限公司赔偿原告张万利三倍购车款共计八十四万元，限本判决生效之日起三十日内履行完毕； \n　　　　二、被告贵州瑞安汽车销售服务有限公司承担连带清偿责任；\n　　　　三、被告沛县宝通汽车销售有限公司和一汽大众汽车有限公司在本案中不承担责任；\n　　　　四、驳回原告张万利的其他诉讼请求。\n　　　　案件受理费12544元，由原告张万利承担544元，被告贵州福泉小河口汽贸有限公司承担12000元。', 'First, by the Guizhou Fuquan small estuary Qimao Limited Compensation to the plaintiff Zhang Wanli three times Car Buying totaling eight hundred and forty thousand yuan, limited to thirty days fulfilled the effective date of the decision; two, the Guizhou Ruian car sales Services Limited joint liability; three, the defendant Peixian Baotong Automobile Sales Co. Ltd. and FAW FAW-Volkswagen Automobile Co disclaims responsibility in this case; four, Zhang Wanli dismissed the plaintiff\'s other claims. The case acceptance fee of 12544 yuan, 544 yuan borne by the plaintiff Zhang Wanli, the defendant Guizhou Fuquan small estuary Qimao Limited bear 12000 yuan.', '贵州瑞安汽车销售有限公司', 'Guizhou Ruian Car Sale Co., Ltd.', 0xE585A8E983A8E69CAAE5B1A5E8A18C, 'All unfulfilled', '（2015）福商初字第347号民事判决', '(2015) the civil judgment of the first word no. 347th', '福泉市人民法院', 'Fuquan City People\'s court', '1460908800000', '贵州', null, null, '1455724800000', '其它规避执行', 'Other circumvention', 'c2016522702zhi157_t20160218_pgzraqcxsyxgs@AVuf1Mxwz6pKxOU1_Khx', '32175761-0', null, null, '2017-04-24 19:59:09', '504');
