INSERT INTO `sxgg` VALUES ('622', '0', '449', '449', null, null, '（2015）顺执字第01741号', '(2015) Shun Xing No. 01741', '判决如下： 1被告一汽-大众汽车有限公司赔偿原告李翠芳车辆损失及车辆缴纳增值税、购置税损失共计十万零六千七百二十七元，于本判决生效之日起七日内给付； 2驳回原告李翠芳的其他诉讼请求。 如果未按本判决指定的期间履行给付金钱义务，应当依照《中华人民共和国民事诉讼法》第二百五十三条之规定，加倍支付迟延履行期间的债务利息。 案件受理费二千七百四十元，由被告一汽-大众汽车有限公司负担，于本判决生效之日起七日内交纳。 如不服本判决，可在判决书送达之日起十五日内，向本院递交上诉状，并按对方当事人的人数提出副本，交纳上诉案件受理费，上诉于北京市第三中级人民法院。上诉期满后七日内仍未交纳上诉案件受理费的，按自动撤回上诉处理。', 'The judgment as follows: 1 the FAW FAW-Volkswagen Automobile Co to compensate the plaintiff Li Cuifang loss of vehicle and vehicle pay value-added tax, purchase tax losses totaling one hundred and six thousand seven hundred and twenty-seven yuan, from the entry into force of this decision within seven days from the date of payment; 2 other plaintiff Li Cuifang rejected the request. In the event of failure to perform the obligation of payment of money in accordance with the provisions of this judgment, it shall pay the interest on the debt during the delay in performance in accordance with the provisions of article 253rd of the Civil Procedure Law of the people\'s Republic of china. Case handling fee of two thousand seven hundred and forty yuan, the defendant by the FAW - FAW-Volkswagen Automobile Co burden, the date of entry into force of the decision to pay within seven days. Who disagrees with this decision, the verdict can be delivered within fifteen days from the date of the petition submitted to this court, and put forward a copy number according to the other party to pay the fees for accepting the case, the appeal, appeal to the Beijing third intermediate people\'s court. Within seven days after the expiration of the appeal has not yet paid the fee for accepting the case, according to the automatic withdrawal of appeal.', '一汽—大众汽车有限公司', 'Faw - Public Car Co., Ltd.', 0xE585A8E983A8E69CAAE5B1A5E8A18C, 'All unfulfilled', '(2014)顺民初字第00476号', '(2014) subject No. No. 00476', '北京市顺义区人民法院', 'Shunyi District Beijing people\'s court', '1427212800000'